                        <interp inst="t18410614-name-380" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM MOTT</persName>
                  </hi>. I was in the Park—this is my handkerchief—missed it from my pocket.</p>
               <p>(The prisoners received good characters.)</p>
